<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551648>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. ML molecular phylogenies generated for this study using the RRGS method GBS. On the left is a phylogeny of the ant genus Cephalotes and the outgroup Procryptocerus.This Cephalotes topology including all samples that had sufficient data generated for our analyses. On the right is the full phylogeny of all samples included for our analysis of the ant genus Polyrhachis, along with the outgroup Camponotus. Both phylogenies were inferred from Illumina data generated from GBS libraries and were inferred using RAxML. Nodes with ML bootstrap support>0.95 are represented by black dots on nodes." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4551648/files/figure.png" .

